DRAW RESULT OF Rs.200/- DENOMINATION NATIONAL PRIZE BONDS-97th DRAW
The 97th Draw of Rs.200/- denomination National Prize Bonds was held today the 15th March, 2024 (Friday) at 9:00 a.m. at State Bank of Pakistan, SBP BSC (Bank), Muzaffarabad. Mr. Waqar Farooq Abbasi Advocate, General Secretary Central Bar, Muzaffarabad presided over the event.
